3. Zero-Trust Secrets Rotation (Vault)

	Static database credentials stored in Kubernetes secrets are a major security risk.


	import hvac # HashiCorp Vault client
	
	client = hvac.Client(url='https://vault.internal:8200', token='s.XXXX')
	
	def rotate_db_credentials(role_name):
	    # Generate dynamic creds from Vault DB engine
	    new_creds = client.secrets.database.generate_credentials(name=role_name)
	    username = new_creds['data']['username']
	    password = new_creds['data']['password']
	    
	    # Logic to update K8s Secret via kubernetes-python-client
